-- 
2011-08-01T03:10:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-01/suzlon-to-raise-50-billion-rupees-selling-bonds-shares-overseas.html
Suzlon Energy Ltd. (SUEL)  plans to raise up
to 50 billion rupees selling shares or bonds overseas, the
company said in a statement to the BSE Ltd. today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
